# Project Development Workflow

## Documentation Review
- Read `@INSTRUCTIONS.md` before starting any task and update it after completion
- Understand project objectives and current status

## Task Execution
- Follow specifications in documentation
- Adhere to project guidelines
- Implement changes as specified

## Post-Task Updates
- Update `@INSTRUCTIONS.md` for architecture changes
- Ensure documentation remains the source of truth

## Code Organization
- Follow established code organization patterns
